    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. those are the core pillars for sure. can you expand more on the 'rule of law' part of that? specifically how proponents argue that failing to enforce immigration laws actually undermines the legitimacy of the entire legal system? i want my students to be able to explain the philosophical connection between border enforcement and the stability of a nation's domestic laws.",
